                      How customer reviews and ratings work

                      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

                      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

                      Cat D
                      4.0 out of 5 stars 4.5/5 Because of Sizing
                      Reviewed in the United States on October 27, 2022
                      Color: Color Block 2Size: SmallVerified Purchase
                      I would give this product 5 stars because the quality is absolutely amazing, especially for hit and miss Amazon. I wore this sweater in 45 degree windy Chicago and was totally fine without a jacket. However, it loses at least half a star because of the sizing issues. As fellow tall people have said in reviews, it cant be worn as a dress or sweater over leggings like some influencers show. Im 57, 36DD, usually 14/XL and since this is oversized, I got a Small and Medium. The M was huge but barely went over my butt. The small fit oversized in the way that I wanted, but hits at about halfway up my butt. So if you are tall and want to wear it with leggings, you need really thick/structured leggings for it to work. With all of that said, Im definitely keeping the sweater and may even get another color! I got so many compliments and it is just beautiful. I just wish it was a bit longer!
